FY_TILE_MINICITY_V1: The start of the new generation of CS:S maps: Tile

Made by: XxDementeixX
Tested by: Kaldmar, Jack The Pumpkin King, and Aeroninja
Theme: Tile
Studio: Riot Designs

This is hopefully the beginning of tile textured maps to expand into a great amount of these maps. They are fun to work with and just getting perfect dimensions with these get your mood to be: professional. Go ahead and try just only using tile textures, hehehe. Well, anyhow, please enjoy my new map and the current brightness level that just makes the whole ground level sparkle.
